# Global snippets

snippet date shows the year, month and day	
	`strftime("%Y-%m-%d")`
snippet ddate
	`strftime("%B %d, %Y")`
snippet diso
	`strftime("%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S")`
snippet time
	`strftime("%H:%M")`
snippet datetime
	`strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M")`
